verbose_text: Attempts to study these conformational changes using 1 H NMR spectroscopy were hampered by the different solubility profiles of the free ligands 3 and 4 compared to the complexes 3.Zn II and 4.Zn II, and the fact that the NMR spectra of the zinc complexes are complicated by the aza-macrocycle adopting multiple geometries upon metal binding (see Sections 14 and 15 in the Supporting Information).
